<br>
Hello guys,<br>
<br>
  I have no idea if any of these email addresses will actually get through, but lets hope one does.  Please forward to the appropriate authority if you don't handle stuff like this.<br>
<br>
  Let me try to be as brief as possible as I am sure you are rather busy folks.<br>
<br>
  I am the author of EQAnnounce, aka Glimwin Nettlefoot of the Xev server.<br>
<br>
  I am writing you this email to get an idea if a program I have written violates *in any way* the EULA.  I do not believe that it does, but I would like your assessment and feedback.  I disclose my in-game name as I would rather this all be an &quot;above-board&quot; discussion.<br>
<br>
